        <div class="agreement" style="display: block;">
            <div id="listThree">
                <div class="Section0" style="layout-grid:15.6000pt;"><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">   </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">温馨提示</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">   </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">1、证券交易业务具有高风险性，不适合于利用养老基金、举借债务、银行贷款等方式取得资金进行投资的实盘点买人。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">   </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">2、证券交易业务只适合于以下实盘点买人：</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">   </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">(1)年满18周岁并具有完全民事行为能力的中国公民；</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">   </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">(2)能够充分理解有关于此交易的一切风险，并且具有风险承受能力的实盘点买人；</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">   </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">(3)愿意承担投资产生的风险。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">   </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><br></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">   </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">尊敬的实盘点买人：</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">   </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">本平台提醒您以下可能导致您本金亏损或超过原始本金损失等风险事项：</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">   </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">1、市场风险</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">   </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">证券市场价格因受各种因素的影响而引发的波动，将使您投资的股票资产面临潜在的风险。市场风险体现为股票投资风险，主要包括：</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">   </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">1）国家货币政策、财政政策、产业政策等变化对证券市场产生一定的影响，导致市场价格水平波动的风险；</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">   </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">2）宏观经济运行周期性波动，对股票市场的收益水平产生影响的风险；</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">   </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">3）上市公司的经营状况受多种因素影响，如市场、技术、竞争、管理、财务等都会导致公司盈利发生变化，从而导致股票价格变动的风险。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">   </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">以上市场风险，实盘点买人在实际操作中难以全面把握，因而存在出现投资失误的可能性，如果不能有效控制风险，则可能遭受较大的损失，实盘点买人必须独自承担由此导致的一切损失。因此，建议实盘点买人时刻保持理性投资，避免过度投机。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">   </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">2、交易风险</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">   </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">(1)实盘点买人需要了解交易具有低保证金和高杠杆比例投资的特点，可能导致快速的盈利或者亏损。若建仓的方向与行情的波动相反，会造成较大的亏损。且平台提供的止盈/止损功能，仅指当行情价到达止盈/止损价时，平台会自动向交易所提交平仓申请，实际平仓价格以在交易所成交价格为准。当行情波动较大时，实际成交价可能高于/低于止盈/止损价，实盘点买人必须承担由此造成的全部损失。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">   </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">(2)平台提供的证券交易均以对应的证券交易所行情价格为基础，连续报出交易所的人民币的买入价或卖出价。该价格可能会因网络等因素与其他途径的报价存在微弱的差距，本平台并不能保证其交易价格与其他市场保持完全一致性。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">   </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">(3) 实盘点买人在本平台的交易系统内，一旦提交订单并成功，即不可撤销，实盘点买人必须接受这种方式可能带来的风险。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">   </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">(4)本平台及其工作人员不会对实盘点买人做出获利保证或做出不会亏损的承诺，并且不会与实盘点买人分享收益或共担风险。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">   </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">(5) 实盘点买人的成交单据均由其本人自主决定。本平台及其员工、视频直播间证券分析师等方式提供的任何关于市场的分析和信息，仅供实盘点买人参考，同时也不构成任何要约。如实盘点买人根据前述参考信息进行交易，由此而造成的交易风险由实盘点买人自行承担。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">   </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">3、技术风险</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">   </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">此业务通过电子通讯技术和互联网技术来实现。有关服务及软、硬件服务由不同的供应商提供，可能会存在品质和稳定性方面的风险；本平台及其工作人员不能控制电讯信号的强弱，也不能保证交易客户端的设备配置或者连接的稳定性以及互联网传播和接收的实时性。故由以上通讯或网络故障导致的某些服务中断或延时可能会对实盘点买人的投资产生影响。另外，实盘点买人的电脑系统可能被病毒或网络黑客攻击，从而使实盘点买人决策无法正确或及时执行。对于上述不确定因素的出现也存在着一定的风险，有可能会对实盘点买人的投资产生影响，实盘点买人应该充分了解并承担由此造成的全部损失。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">   </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">4、不可抗力风险</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">   </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">任何因交易所不能够控制的原因，包括但不仅限于地震、水灾、火灾、暴动、罢工、战争、政府管制、国际或国内的禁止或者限制以及停电、技术故障、电子故障等其它无法预测和防范的不可抗事件，都有可能会对实盘点买人的交易产生影响，实盘点买人应该充分了解并承担由此造成的全部损失。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">   </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">特别提示</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">   </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">1、实盘点买人在参与之前务必详尽的了解证券投资的基本知识和相关风险以及交易所有关的业务规则等，依法从事证券投资业务。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">   </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">2、本平台与现有的国内其他证券交易平台相比，在交易模式、交易规则等方面存在着一定的差别</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;background:rgb(255,255,0);mso-shading:rgb(255,255,0);">(详情请查阅《实盘点买人与实盘出借人合作协议》及《实盘点买人参与证券交易合作涉及费用及资费标准》，具体以平台实际公布信息为准。)</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">；而且本平台为了确保市场</font>“公开、公平、公正”和健康稳定地发展，将采取更加严格的措施，强化市场的监管。请您务必密切关注有关于该市场的公告、风险提示等信息，及时了解市场风险状况，做到理性投资，切忌盲目跟风。本平台只提供撮合实盘点买人交易，实盘点买人应为自身的交易行为结果负责。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">   </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:a